### ============================================================
### Payments
### Base URL: https://localhost:49609
###
### Payment is auto-created when an order is placed (via OrderPlacedHandler).
### To get the payment Guid token, call GET /api/orders/{orderId} after checkout confirm
### — the response includes a non-null paymentUrl when status is "Placed".
###
### Flow:
###   1. POST /api/checkout/confirm  → { orderId }          (presale.http)
###   2. GET  /api/orders/{orderId}  → { ..., paymentUrl }  (sales-orders.http)
###   3. Extract Guid from paymentUrl → use below to fetch payment details
###   4. Complete payment via Web UI at the paymentUrl
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = https://localhost:49609
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
@contentType = application/json

# ============================================================
# AUTH
# ============================================================

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@localhost",
  "password": "aDminN@W25!"
}

###

# ============================================================
# PAYMENTS — own-scoped by Guid token
# ============================================================

### Get payment by Guid token (own-scoped)
# Expected: 200 OK  →  PaymentDetailsVm
# paymentId: Guid extracted from the paymentUrl returned by GET /api/orders/{orderId}
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get payment — not found / not owned by current user
# Expected: 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payments/ffffffff-ffff-ffff-ffff-ffffffffffff
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
